data.description: No compromises with this one! You get to have your cake and eat it too! Is it privacy that you desire? Room for a few horses or cattle? A large, exquisitely maintained home that boasts an open floor plan and natural light? Maybe you need a separate living space for a family member under the same roof? This showstopper sitting on 37 acres offers all of that and SO MUCH MORE! This picturesque home greets you from the top of the hill at the end of a long, winding driveway. Every detail was well thought out all the way down to the unique concrete work around the home! The foyer leads to a stunning living room, complete with a wall of windows reaching all of the way to the wood cathedral ceiling! The kitchen boasts a double oven, a glass cooktop, an island and an abundance of counter/cabinet space. The main suite is located on the entry level and is not lacking in size in any area- bedroom, closet or bathroom! Double vanities, lots of cabinet space, tiled walk-in shower, claw foot soaking tub, and natural light make this bathroom one to envy!
